headline: The Cigna Group Foundation Commits Additional $1M to Boys & Girls Clubs of America to Support Youth Mental Health
summary: As part of The Cigna Group's (NYSE: CI) multiyear commitment to improve youth mental health, The Cigna Group Foundation announced a $1 million contribution over the next two years to Boys & Girls Clubs of America.
